BLAST (Basic Local Alignment Search Tool)
## 📌 Purpose

BLAST compares biological sequences to identify similarities.

## 📌 Types of BLAST
BLASTn
BLASTp
BLASTx
tBLASTn
tBLASTx

##📌 Key Parameters
E-value
Query coverage
Identity percentage
Score

##📌 Applications
Homology search
Functional prediction
Species identification
Conserved sequence analysis

## 📌 Important Outputs
Alignment table
Similarity scores
Pairwise alignment

